----
# ptui / psh-tui
- micro-sized tui lib in pure sh
## Functions
- hline
  -- create a line $1 in length using $2/- with $3 indentation
  -- does NOT create a new line
- vline
  -- create a line $1 tall with $2 indentation from $3/| 
  -- creates new line
- dvline
  -- creates 2 lines $1 with $2 indentation from $3/| $3 apart
  -- creates new line
- rec 
  -- makes a fucking rectangle
  ---- $1 indentation
  ---- $2 wide (-1)
  ---- $3 tall (-1)
  ---- $4/- char to use for top and bottom
  ---- $5/| char to use for sides
  ---- $6 disable + corners if 0
